
# Sheep Fight

## Project Overview
Sheep Fight is a two-player competitive game developed using SFML (Simple and Fast Multimedia Library), featuring strategic animal-based gameplay.

## Prerequisites

### Dependencies
- C++ compiler (supporting C++11 or later)
- SFML Library
- Make

### Installation

1. Install SFML:
```bash
# On Ubuntu/Debian
sudo apt-get install libsfml-dev

# On macOS with Homebrew
brew install sfml

# On Windows, download from SFML website and set up manually
```

2. Compile the project:
```bash
make
```

